These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-1::.
Hobby: hiking, reading, skydiving, writing
Birthday: june, december, july, august
Game: monopoly, scrabble, billiard, chess
1. Game:monopoly == Hobby:writing##1
2. Game:billiard is on the left of Birthday:december##1
3. Hobby:writing is in an odd position##4
4. Game:scrabble is on the left or right of Game:chess##3
5. Birthday:july is on the left or right of Hobby:hiking##3
6. Game:chess is on the left of Hobby:skydiving##1
7. Game:scrabble is on the far left or far right##3
8. Game:chess is between Birthday:august and Hobby:hiking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |   2    |    3    |     4     |
| Hobby         | writing      | hiking | reading | skydiving |
| Birthday   | july | june  | december   | august    |
| Game     | monopoly     | billiard    | chess    | scrabble      |

