1. City:venice is on the left or right of Hobby:sudoku##3
2. Hobby:video-games == Movie-Genre:spy##1
3. Hobby:sudoku is in an even position##4
4. City:nizza is on the far right##1
5. City:berlin is on the far left##1
6. Hobby:singing is on the left of Movie-Genre:animation##1
7. Movie-Genre:drama is between Hobby:video-games and Hobby:singing##2
8. Movie-Genre:thriller is between Movie-Genre:animation and Hobby:sudoku##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Hobby         | video-games | sudoku   | singing | dancing  |
| Movie-Genre   | spy     | drama | thriller  | animation |
| City     | berlin        | london  | venice    | nizza |

