.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-3::.
Pet: goldfish, turtle, frog, snake
Hobby: traveling, woodworking, skydiving, video-games
Transport: motorbike, roller, snowmobile, train
1. Hobby:video-games is between Pet:goldfish and Pet:snake##2
2. Hobby:woodworking == Transport:train##1
3. Transport:motorbike == Pet:frog##1
4. Transport:motorbike is on the right of Pet:snake##1
5. Pet:snake is in an odd position##4
6. Hobby:skydiving is between Pet:turtle and Hobby:traveling##2
7. Hobby:video-games is on the left of Transport:snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Pet          | goldfish | turtle   | snake     | frog     |
| Hobby   | woodworking  | video-games | skydiving   | traveling  |
| Transport     | train      | roller | snowmobile | motorbike |

